<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="exciting-adj">exciting <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪk'saɪtɪŋ/    美 /ɪk'saɪtɪŋ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>令人兴奋的；使人激动的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The idea was so exciting. 
这主意真令人激动。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The marathon is an exciting event in any year. 
马拉松比赛无论在哪一年都是一件令人兴奋的体育赛事。</p><footer>2008 广东</footer></div></div>